Installation Instructions
*************************

Basic Installation
==================

The CMake build system is needed for the installation to work. Download
the newest version at www.cmake.org or use your distribution package
manager. Briefly, these commands generate Makefile, build and install
this package:

    cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release .
    make
    make install

For additional information, see:
http://www.cmake.org/cmake/help/documentation.html
